languages.text: {n}Эльдарка стоит поодаль, скрестив тонкие руки на груди. Ее взгляд полон решимости и направлен прямо на Инквизитора Калькасара. Даже если ваши слова и коснулись ее слуха, она не подает виду.{/n}

languages.text: {n}Yrliet is standing at a distance, with her slender arms crossed over her chest. Her gaze is resolute and aimed straight at Inquisitor Calcazar. Even if your words have reached her ears, she does not show it.{/n}

languages.text: {n}Yrliet se tient à l'écart, ses bras minces croisés sur la poitrine. Son regard résolu ne quitte pas l'inquisiteur Calcazar. Si vos paroles sont parvenues jusqu'à ses oreilles, elle ne le montre pas.{/n}

languages.text: {n}伊莉耶特站在远处，瘦长的双臂交叉叠在胸前。她的目光坚定，直直地盯着大审判官卡尔卡扎。即便她真的听到了你的话，恐怕也不会有任何反应。{/n}

traits.locale_text: {n}伊莉耶特站在远处，瘦弱的双臂交叉在胸前。她的目光坚定，直直地盯着卡尔卡扎审判长。即便她真的听到了你的话，恐怕也不会有任何反应。{/n}
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: {n}ユリエットはスレンダーな腕を胸の上で組み、離れたところに立っている。彼女の目は毅然としており、まっすぐカルカサル異端審問官に向けられている。あなたの言葉が耳に届いたとしても、彼女は反応を見せないだろう。{/n}
languages.original_text: {n}Yrliet is standing at a distance, with her slender arms crossed over her chest. Her gaze is resolute and aimed straight at Inquisitor Calcazar. Even if your words have reached her ears, she does not show it.{/n}

languages.text: {n}Yrliet steht in einigem Abstand von dir, die schlanken Arme vor der Brust verschränkt. Ihr entschlossener Blick ist direkt auf Inquisitor Calcazar gerichtet. Selbst wenn deine Worte zu ihr durchgedrungen sind, sie zeigt es nicht.{/n}
languages.original_text: {n}Yrliet is standing at a distance, with her slender arms crossed over her chest. Her gaze is resolute and aimed straight at Inquisitor Calcazar. Even if your words have reached her ears, she does not show it.{/n}

languages.text: {n}Yrliet está de pie a cierta distancia de ti, con los esbeltos brazos cruzados sobre el pecho. Su mirada es decidida y está centrada en el inquisidor Calcazar. Si tus palabras han llegado a sus oídos, desde luego no lo demuestra.{/n}

languages.text: {n}Yrliet, ince kollarını göğsünde kavuşturmuş hâlde uzakta dikiliyor. Bakışları kararlı ve direkt olarak Engizisyoncu Calcazar'a odaklı. Sözcüklerin kulağına eriştiyse bile belli etmiyor.{/n}
